{"tid":1486693,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[多圖] 大波女警j到我無曬紙巾","createTime":"2019-08-19T03:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T17:44:57.000Z","uid":93124,"like":46,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8ceaf2dcddeef1dc6ffc63b055b877f2962091fd","tid":1486693,"uid":93124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:07:22.000Z","msg":"唔好意思呃咗大家入黎<br />\n<ins>大家聽住   </ins><br />\n我地要贏 就唔可以 亦都無本錢 再重蹈雨傘既覆轍<br />\n所以 唔好比昨日既美好景象衝昏頭腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如:<br />\n1. 見到越黎越多大陸人支持香港人和平示威, 就打曬飛機, 開始同意以後只應和理非<br />\n2. 不停睇番昨日170萬人上街既相, 出好多post話覺得我地贏左, 但係無提到揹住官司既手足<br />\n3. 和理非行理無咩cost, 同之前既衝擊畫面相比太唯美, 希望黎緊既行動都唔使衝<br />\n<br />\n我再提提大家 我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">停戰一日</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警就多一日時間睇CCTV同搜證, 拉人<br />\n我地<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">停戰一個禮拜</span></span><br />\n黑警就多一個禮拜時間睇CCTV同搜證, 拉人<br />\n我地停戰兩個禮拜 呢場運動就會慢慢玩完 <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">最後咩都唔會得到</span><br />\n<br />\n所以我呼籲各位手足開心完, 休息完, 盡快歸位<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>設死線! 再佈陣! </strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我地唔可以比倦怠感擊敗!!!!<br />\n香港人 唔好輸!!!! <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f8f2a151290cbc2fff5bd79fc727cf47ef5383","tid":1486693,"uid":93124,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:08:04.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"4e14e3f7470c221beeedab6a93891ccd71720ec8","tid":1486693,"uid":208452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:08:13.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港自由之書&mdash;賣卡投